sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Controller as kserve-controller-manager<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KnativeSvc as Knative Serving
    participant StorageInit as storage-initializer<br/>(Init Container)
    participant S3 as Cloud Storage (S3/GCS)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: InferenceService Deployment (Serverless Mode)
    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event: InferenceService created<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Knative Service<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>KnativeSvc: Reconcile Knative Service
    KnativeSvc->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment + Revision
    StorageInit->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>Auth: IAM / Secret credentials
    S3-->>StorageInit: Model artifacts
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create VirtualService +<br/>ExternalName Service

    participant Client as External Client
    participant IstioGW as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant VS as VirtualService Routing
    participant KnativeGW as Knative Local Gateway<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant Pod as Model Serving Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS

    Note over Client,Pod: Flow 2: Inference Request (Serverless Mode)
    Client->>IstioGW: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token (optional)
    IstioGW->>VS: Route via VirtualService<br/>mTLS (Istio mesh)
    VS->>KnativeGW: Forward to local gateway<br/>HTTP, mTLS
    KnativeGW->>Pod: Inference request<br/>HTTP/8080, mTLS
    Pod-->>KnativeGW: Prediction response
    KnativeGW-->>VS: Response
    VS-->>IstioGW: Response
    IstioGW-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS

    participant GW as Gateway (HTTPRoute)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant EPP as EPP Scheduler<br/>9002/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant LLMPod as LLM Serving Pod<br/>8000/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client,LLMPod: Flow 3: LLMInferenceService with Inference Scheduling
    Client->>GW: Inference request<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token (optional)
    GW->>EPP: ext_proc request<br/>gRPC/9002, TLS (self-signed)
    EPP->>LLMPod: Query InferencePool targets<br/>HTTP/8000
    LLMPod-->>EPP: Endpoint metrics
    EPP-->>GW: Selected target endpoint
    GW->>LLMPod: Forward to selected pod<br/>HTTP/8000
    LLMPod-->>GW: Inference response
    GW-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS
